```

## Backend Structure (api/)

### Main Entry Points
- `main.py` - FastAPI application entry point, route registration, middleware setup
- `config.py` - Application configuration from environment variables
- `database.py` - MongoDB/Beanie database connection and initialization
- `dependencies.py` - Shared dependencies (auth helpers, permission checkers)

### Core Directories

#### models/ - Beanie ODM Models
Database models with automatic validation and type safety:
- `base_model.py` - Base document class with common fields (id, timestamps)
- `client_account_model.py` - Multi-tenant client organizations
- `user_model.py` - User accounts with profile and permissions
- `role_model.py` - RBAC roles with hierarchical permissions
- `group_model.py` - User groups for bulk permission assignment
- `permission_model.py` - Permission definitions and hierarchy
- `refresh_token_model.py` - JWT refresh token storage
- `password_reset_token_model.py` - Password reset functionality
- `scopes.py` - Permission scope constants and utilities

#### routes/ - API Endpoints
FastAPI route handlers with dependency injection:
- `auth_routes.py` - Authentication (login, logout, refresh, password reset)
- `user_routes.py` - User CRUD operations
- `role_routes.py` - Role management
- `group_routes.py` - Group management
- `permission_routes.py` - Permission listing and management
- `client_account_routes.py` - Client organization management
- `platform_routes.py` - Platform-level administration

#### services/ - Business Logic
Service layer handling complex operations:
- `user_service.py` - User management logic
- `role_service.py` - Role operations and permission handling
- `group_service.py` - Group membership management
- `permission_service.py` - Permission validation and hierarchy
- `security_service.py` - Password hashing, JWT tokens
- `refresh_token_service.py` - Token lifecycle management
- `client_account_service.py` - Multi-tenant operations

#### schemas/ - Pydantic Models
Request/response validation schemas:
- `auth_schema.py` - Login, token, password reset DTOs
- `user_schema.py` - User creation, update, response models
- `role_schema.py` - Role DTOs with permission lists
- `group_schema.py` - Group management schemas
- `permission_schema.py` - Permission structure schemas
- `client_account_schema.py` - Client organization schemas
- `refresh_token_schema.py` - Token response models
- `password_reset_schema.py` - Password reset flow schemas

#### middleware/
Custom middleware components:
- `rate_limiting.py` - Request rate limiting for security

